data.description: Tired of high interest rates? Take a look at 217 Morning Song with an assumable 2.25% VA loan! It is a spacious 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home featuring a loft. It's just the right size to fulfill all your needs without excess. The welcoming backyard provides ample space for various outdoor activities, from bocce ball and grilling to gardening. What's more, this home comes with brand new, fully paid off solar panels, adding to its appeal.Nestled in Summers Corner, soon home to the largest amenity center in Charleston. Don't hesitate any longer - it's time to embrace the quality of life you truly deserve.
